PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Analytics App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is a blockchain analytics app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: A blockchain analytics app helps users analyze and gain insights from blockchain data. It allows tracking transactions, wallets, smart contracts and more on various blockchains.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What blockchains does your app support?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app currently supports analysis of Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchains. We are continuously working to add support for more networks.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of analysis can I perform?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You can analyze transaction flows, track wallet balances over time, monitor smart contract activity, identify potential fraudulent behavior, and much more using our powerful analytics tools.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is your app suitable for businesses?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our blockchain analytics suite is perfect for businesses that need to analyze blockchain data for compliance, forensics, customer intelligence and other enterprise use cases.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our blockchain data analysis platform
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Blockchain analytics refers to the process of parsing, analyzing and interpreting data from blockchain networks to gain insights into on-chain activity, identify patterns and trends, and monitor transactions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What blockchain networks do you support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our platform currently supports analysis of data from Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other major public blockchain networks. We are constantly working to expand our coverage.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can blockchain analytics be used?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Common use cases include transaction monitoring for compliance, investigative analytics for criminal investigations, business intelligence and market insights, and tracking asset flows across wallets and exchanges.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the data updated in real-time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our platform ingests and parses new blockchain data as soon as it is confirmed on the network, providing you with up-to-the-second insights and analytics.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How do I get started with your platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: You can sign up for a free trial on our website to explore the platform's features. Our customer success team is also available to provide guidance and onboarding support.
